Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, housemate, Erica on Tuesday lamented that her love interest, Kiddwaya was upset with her. Erica disclosed that Kiddwaya was upset with her because of her disappointing performance during the Airtel task. During the task, Erica was caught laughing at her group’s performance. However, speaking with fellow housemates, Tolanibaj and Trikytee after the task, Erica explained that she was laughing because she was nervous. According to Erica: “Kiddwaya is upset with me because of our performance, I was nervous and that’s why I was laughing during the performance.” She apologised to Kiddwaya for disappointing the team.